              <div class="clearfix"></div>
            </ul>
          </div>
                              <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-main"> <a class="ebma-anchor0" href="#" id="p1"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-main"><i></i><span class="head-con">前言篇</span></h4>
          </div>
          <div><p>
                            <span style="font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:normal;">最近几次乘坐公交车总会听到龙山蜡像馆的广告，很是好奇，石家庄啥时候也开了个蜡像馆？虽然我个人对蜡像馆之类的场馆不感兴趣，但谁让我是一个好奇宝宝呢。就这样在好奇心的驱使下，吃过午饭，从单位开溜，一睹龙山蜡像馆真容。</span>
                                              </p>
          </div>
                              <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-main"> <a class="ebma-anchor0" href="#" id="p2"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-main"><i></i><span class="head-con">行程篇</span></h4>
          </div>
          <div><p>
                            <p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">龙山蜡像馆位于石家庄鹿泉区东鲍庄村，距市区大约30公里，沿着石清路一路向西就可以到，非常好找。老司机开车40分钟就能到，新手那就没准了。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/a74afe751ae62087b86ccc21020583a0.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/a74afe751ae62087b86ccc21020583a0.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">不得不说，自从石清路修好之后，路况好多了，记得去年走这条路去平山的时候那叫一个痛苦，坑坑洼洼、颠颠簸簸，最头疼的是堵堵堵，那叫一个窝火。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">自驾出去游玩，我的一贯原则就是车上可劲补觉，下车使劲折腾。所以路上发生了什么我根本不知道，我只知道我睡醒的时候就已经到景区了。<br></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">景区停车场背靠大山，山上有一个红色的龙的图案，越看越像plus版的剪纸。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/a60a4017ddcdee79654dc565f15f2abc.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/a60a4017ddcdee79654dc565f15f2abc.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">售票中心，我们从网上团购的门票，通票50元，直接到窗口兑换纸质门票就可以，非常方便。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/64935946e9eebaddc5538476727332b7.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/64935946e9eebaddc5538476727332b7.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">进入景区大门，左手边是景区餐厅，两层小白楼，由于我们是吃过饭才过来的所以没有进去参观。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/153a613358effe58d87d8b924b748ddf.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/153a613358effe58d87d8b924b748ddf.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">右手边有一小段楼梯连接一条桥，穿过就正式进入园区。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/b8b2b779a68d43891b8bb0ddfa80c598.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/b8b2b779a68d43891b8bb0ddfa80c598.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">桥的右边就是大名鼎鼎的滑草区，说是滑草，其实铺的是假的草坪，不过丝毫不影响游玩的乐趣。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/9b858d39bc0b1a4ab2f840aa0469546d.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/9b858d39bc0b1a4ab2f840aa0469546d.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">穿过桥有一个指示牌，告诉游客不同游乐项目的具体位置。由于天气太热，所以我们计划先去参观室内的蜡像馆，然后再游玩室外的项目。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/83a0d403ec58b7bdaf4047cc06adb44b.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/83a0d403ec58b7bdaf4047cc06adb44b.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">两边郁郁葱葱的小树遮住了刺眼的太阳，走在树下有点小凉爽。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/ab171e6ac23da321130a13acbe4c4924.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/ab171e6ac23da321130a13acbe4c4924.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">往前走直接到达燕赵历史名人画廊，里边讲述了25位燕赵历史名人的故事，绝对寓教于乐的好地方。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/84c35c2635fdd608eb1015cfa9f591b1.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/84c35c2635fdd608eb1015cfa9f591b1.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">长长的走廊一眼望不到头，走廊两边种有杏、核桃、柿子等各种果树，有兴趣的话可以过来采摘。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/9d74e1a8cdbc2157da4c478956deb570.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/9d74e1a8cdbc2157da4c478956deb570.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">燕赵历史名人之扁鹊的故事，首先想到四个字：望闻问切，至于其余的，就不要再问我这个学渣了。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/6282d2a94f43126d5fd5bb89e913b48f.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/6282d2a94f43126d5fd5bb89e913b48f.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">路边的石头上写有各种名人名言，真是抓住一切机会对我们进行教育啊~</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/281dc0a00797fa8b4ad6444d134da8ed.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/281dc0a00797fa8b4ad6444d134da8ed.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">穿过国学走廊就到了名人民俗蜡像馆，看名字就知道肯定是和民俗相关的，那些想看冰冰、凡凡、峰峰、炅炅等蜡像的人就不要过来了。<br></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/7280b86ba6030a8e804992299887b749.JPG" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/7280b86ba6030a8e804992299887b749.JPG"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">进入场馆，首先看到这一名白衣红裙的汉美人蜡像，这是一个高仿真机器人迎宾小姐，全天候为游客迎宾、讲解。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/f573c76cd1f9aedaab5784da2562dfb0.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/f573c76cd1f9aedaab5784da2562dfb0.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">这个门设计的有意思，刚开始吓我一跳，怎么刚进来就无路可走了，走过去才发现是声控的，中间的石头自动滑向两边，然后你就穿越啦。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/8c62486e80e0030352bb965465d64d6e.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/8c62486e80e0030352bb965465d64d6e.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">蜡像馆内的所有蜡像都取材于中华传统文化的远古传说、经典故事、励志成语，有“开天辟地”创世宫、“孝感动天”孝道馆、“一诺千金”诚信阁等6个主题分馆，展现了女娲造人、卧冰求鲤、韩信报恩、梁祝化蝶、匡衡破墙借光等经典历史故事。&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/9a8b6459e5079972d2bf3ae89769f945.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/9a8b6459e5079972d2bf3ae89769f945.png"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/b7171b33836bf73ba3fe4976de0b83c6.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/b7171b33836bf73ba3fe4976de0b83c6.png"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/e5c603566441162ca1e79efa4ecd40bd.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/e5c603566441162ca1e79efa4ecd40bd.png"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/8ad274427c1a9669bca6de28ea132f6b.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/8ad274427c1a9669bca6de28ea132f6b.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">欣欣同学你不要太调皮，这背篓都能够把你装进去了。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/26dc7ffb6d9b99f19f1f7d47af9644ea.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/26dc7ffb6d9b99f19f1f7d47af9644ea.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">出蜡像馆向左走能到国学大讲堂，我对这些事是一点点兴趣都没有，远观一下就可以了。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/9ad7d9f18263054a5708ee6a0d880c31.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/9ad7d9f18263054a5708ee6a0d880c31.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">紧挨着蜡像馆的是青少年拓展中心，里边的拓展项目超级刺激，至少我没有勇气上去挑战。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/2382d6737b2003862bb64c3f331a44cd.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/2382d6737b2003862bb64c3f331a44cd.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">右边类似于变形金刚的黄蓝灰的建筑物还没有建好，建好之后是VR体验馆，至于什么是VR我就不多做解释，相信你们比我懂。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/1e16257b3a93f0807691545f29ee40b5.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/1e16257b3a93f0807691545f29ee40b5.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">拓展区里边的装备区，头盔、安全绳一样都不能少。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/99648cb70c975853aad59372e1ce803e.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/99648cb70c975853aad59372e1ce803e.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">拓展中心可谓是充分利用了空间，上边是拓展项目，下边则是适合小不点玩的游乐园。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/52f223c43a86a17558cd37f11060c9af.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/52f223c43a86a17558cd37f11060c9af.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/8a79e638c8d57f77b7038eb2ede735f4.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/8a79e638c8d57f77b7038eb2ede735f4.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">从拓展中心出来，顺着山路往上走进入室外项目区。首先看到的就是重走长征路，看似简单，但要想走完全程可就难了。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/0599c4ac25cd3dcc65aa48e31350c0df.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/0599c4ac25cd3dcc65aa48e31350c0df.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">重走长征路中最简单的一截——吊起来的木板。我承认我是怂的，只上去走了一步就果断放弃了。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/e013eb8426d18a630da37b05eb3f71fa.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/e013eb8426d18a630da37b05eb3f71fa.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">山路的另一边有一个八卦迷宫阵，走进去绕了半天才绕出来，真有种把篱笆墙拆了的冲动，我这暴脾气啊。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/0ff75d7941583f9c22b7842455f360b0.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/0ff75d7941583f9c22b7842455f360b0.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">心心念念的疯狂大滑梯，走到跟前还真有点害怕了，左边黄色、绿色的是给小朋友玩的，右边三个滑道给成人玩，果断选择成人里边坡度最小的滑道，右边那两个滑道估计能吓屎宝宝。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/fc131be488c445b5af93e0eba1d985eb.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/fc131be488c445b5af93e0eba1d985eb.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">射箭场地，本宝宝投了三次，一次都没有投在靶上，丢人丢到家了。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/14b7a3ca6248fd443db390913218dd4b.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/14b7a3ca6248fd443db390913218dd4b.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">射箭场对面是一块空旷的小树林，有秋千还有供游人休息的小木凳。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/183fad3a6bb8380fea7adf6f2b84a0cb.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/183fad3a6bb8380fea7adf6f2b84a0cb.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">穿过小广场，顺着山路往上走，就到了民俗文化园。大家猜猜下边的家伙什叫什么？反正它认识我，我不认识它~</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/cd95295e0d01743597d5a199561e7d25.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/cd95295e0d01743597d5a199561e7d25.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">这两人彻底玩嗨了，这是要推着下地么~</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/88d992a949d1b4c0c0d772ee94a582d1.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/88d992a949d1b4c0c0d772ee94a582d1.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">民俗馆房顶上挂的这块蓝印花布是我的最爱，好想扯一块回家。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/be198fdb315bc89232d189c4dbd3cc2f.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/be198fdb315bc89232d189c4dbd3cc2f.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">从民俗文化园出来直奔滑草区，在尖叫刺激中我们的龙山蜡像馆之游正式结束。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/53551e672f57e3ba17aae70a3c14a6ea.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/53551e672f57e3ba17aae70a3c14a6ea.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">从蜡像馆出来才四点多，时间尚早，正好再去海岸樱源转一圈。海岸樱源距离龙山蜡像馆也就5公里左右，开车十多分钟到达，非常便利。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/e1ac3a5b3b494fcbaab394eaae12ae3a.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/e1ac3a5b3b494fcbaab394eaae12ae3a.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">水边的小树林，好多人都过来这里烧烤露营。<br></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/2d26a32e826c36c93cefa7fba8d6a5a1.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/2d26a32e826c36c93cefa7fba8d6a5a1.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">水边草丛里的帐篷，在这里露营估计要被蚊子咬死吧。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/a3ea2f2ee5809ab444955531b46c0370.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/a3ea2f2ee5809ab444955531b46c0370.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">岸边有一大片的浅水区，脱掉鞋直接进去嗨，假装去海边。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/1fa33f69c104ecfb8887a58a9a1a7b53.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/1fa33f69c104ecfb8887a58a9a1a7b53.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">造型一定要凹一个，一望无际的水面，是不是很壮观。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/0fcdbba8082e89e9d40325e0d22c29d0.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/0fcdbba8082e89e9d40325e0d22c29d0.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">停在水边的游艇，150块钱一圈，在水面上兜一圈，想想也很爽。</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/790b46cedc937b5cc962a93936fec72a.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/790b46cedc937b5cc962a93936fec72a.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">虽为单身狗，但仍是要秀一把，你牵着我，我牵着你，真爱啊！</p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/bc511185debb4f3658943e9701ae94b9.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/bc511185debb4f3658943e9701ae94b9.png"><img src="http://www.aitto.net/new_uploads/2017/0828/a92591b0f9f908e3368c3965cf31f3ea.png" alt="" title="" _src="/new_uploads/2017/0828/a92591b0f9f908e3368c3965cf31f3ea.png"></p><p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">大约下午五点开始往回走，不上班出去嗨的感觉果真很爽，下次继续出来嗨。</p>                            </p>
          </div>
                              <div class="ebma-chapter chapter-main"> <a class="ebma-anchor0" href="#" id="p3"></a>
            <h4 class="CatalogHd-main"><i></i><span class="head-con">总结篇</span></h4>
          </div>
          <div><p>
                            <span style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;">总之，除了有点热，有点晒之外，整个行程还是比较愉悦的。去之前还在想，自己对龙山蜡像馆可能会一点兴趣都没有，结果却大大出乎我的意料，竟然如此有趣，尤其适合家长带小朋友过来游玩，既可以了解我国历史文化知识又能够强身健体，寓教于乐。</span>                            </p>
          </div>
